history.content:
Schlumberger is partnering with HKN to host an in-person infosession at the Wozniak Lounge on Thursday, Feb 3rd, at 5:30 pm PST. Food is provided! In addition to EECS and L&S CS, they are interested in reaching mechanical engineering, data science and graduate students.

"We are Schlumberger, the leading provider of technology and services to the energy industry. In over 120 countries; we design, develop, and deliver technology that transforms how work is done for a sustainable future.

 

We define the boundaries of the industry by unleashing our talented people’s energy. We’re looking for innovators to join our diverse community of colleagues and develop new solutions, embrace the power of digital, and push the limits of what’s possible. If you share our passion for discovery and want to find out what you could really do, then here is the place to do it."
history.subject: Schlumberger In-Person Infosession (Thursday, 2/3) at the Woz Lounge
